{"tid":1663292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯條例】林鄭：非戀棧權位不排除改組問責班子　願研究不違法治下支援被捕年輕人","createTime":"2019-10-19T10:27:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T12:56:12.000Z","uid":252013,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"dd6fc2f6dec4853f4ce1d5bf80d629cc51c44576","tid":1663292,"uid":252013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T10:27:38.000Z","msg":"其實藍又好黃又好，個個都話佢做得唔好....問責班子都係....就算唔講逃犯條例，最近放寬樓按都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反修訂《逃犯條例》風波觸發多場示威衝突，對於有指特首林鄭月娥應該下台，林鄭月娥今早（19日）出席商台節目時表示，政府想展示有承擔和願意負責任，盡力及盡快處理現時社會問題，強調「我哋唔係為咗戀棧權位」。她說，解決反修例風波後，不排除政府問責班子或行會成員改組可能性。<br />\n她表示，社會出現紛爭，政府責無旁貸，她承認政府工作有改善空間，未能更好掌握民情民意作適當回應。但如今反修例演變成另一回事，有人認為是逆權運動，是為反政府及反政權，亦有人將事件帶至國際層面，更出現令人擔心是違反「一國兩制」、鼓吹港獨的...<a href=\"https://headline.klwpc.com/share.php?a=headlinewwd&amp;id=119135\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fheadline.klwpc.com%2Fshare.php%3Fa%3Dheadlinewwd%26id%3D119135&d=om99xhx1cOxPLv9Q%2FbR%2FoLJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=f83995b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://headline.klwpc.com/share.php?a=headlinewwd&amp;id=119135</a>"},{"pid":"ba636639750930ea09af8f05f8f6b562b8fbb3f7","tid":1663292,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T10:28:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「文宣升級」巴士流動大字報<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1662724\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1662724</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wj3z6Ov.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwj3z6Ov.jpg&h=9f735918&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"4ddc056aaa0844c2659108b4a8ece64583502c19","tid":1663292,"uid":288670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T10:30:17.000Z","msg":"學緊台灣228事件處理手法"},{"pid":"c44e62a11ad19413078969d477090b9821406631","tid":1663292,"uid":276175,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T10:34:23.000Z","msg":"呢件美心西餅幾時先捨得下台？"},{"p